### One liner to check if remote port is open
### this is for when you have nothing else to work with
### only works with tcp
> ref:- https://superuser.com/questions/621870/test-if-a-port-on-a-remote-system-is-reachable-without-telnet 

```
</dev/tcp/localhost/11211 && echo Port is open || echo Port is closed
```
